listing.name: Gorgeous Canalhouse in perfect spot

user.about:
Wij zijn Jorrit Stracke en Dirk Minnebo. Samen runnen wij Iambnb. 
Iambnb verhuurt mensen hun appartementen terwijl zij op vakantie zijn. Op die manier zijn er altijd leuke woningen vrij voor mensen die Amsterdam willen ervaren als een local.  

Dirk heeft rechten gestuurd en ik, Jorrit, voor piloot. Echter hebben we beide voor een andere koers gekozen en hebben wij nu ons eigen bedrijf.

Dirk en ik staan relaxt in het leven en houden van hard werken, maar ook van Amsterdam. Inmiddels beheren wij al ongeveer 60 appartementen in en om Amsterdam! We hebben daarom al veel ervaring en doen ons uiterste best die te gebruiken om uw verblijf bij ons zo aangenaam mogelijk te maken.

Onze hobby's zijn voetbal, filmmaken, uitgaan en andere leuke dingen doen. Natuurlijk is Iambnb ook eigenlijk een hobby, omdat wij dit met zoveel plezier doen.  
Wij kijken er naar uit om u te verwelkomen in Amsterdam!

listing.access: You have access to the whole house with kitchen, bedroom, bathroom and living room. You do not have to share this apartment with others.
listing.description:
This apartment is right were you want to be. On Keizersgracht close to the Amstelriver, you are literally in the centre of everything! The beautiful canals on your doorsteps, quietness in the centre in a beautiful home!

The apartment is quite unique. Right on the canals it's spacious and bright. It has everything you need and you will feel right at home in this classic canalhouse. Don't look in any further, you have found your palace for you holliday.

You have access to the whole house with kitchen, bedroom, bathroom and living room. You do not have to share this apartment with others.

Iambnb will let you in, hand you the keys and show you around in the house and if you like in Amsterdam. After that you can always call if you need any assistance.

The canals of Amsterdam is what makes it the most beautiful city in the world. In addition, the house is so central that you can reach everything by foot. Utrechtsestraat is one of the nicest shopping streets of Amsterdam. This is a 1 minute walk. The same for Carre, Hermitage and Rembrandt. Leidseplein, Dam Square, Red Light District, Anne Frank House, Rijksmuseum and Van Gogh Museum are easy to reach and within 15 minutes walking.

Distance to:
Central Station: 1.5km
Dam: 0.8km
Leidseplein: 1km
Museumplein: 1.8km
Vondelpark: 1.4km

Normal check-in and check-out times:
Check-out  11:00 am.
Check-in  between 13:00 21:00 pm.

For other in- and check-out times please contact us.

Check in after 21:00 is possible but it costs an additional of 20,- euro.
listing.house_rules: Please don't trash the place, don't smoke inside or be loud at night. Other than that, enjoy it as your own apartment.

review.comments:
This apartment is in a fantastic location, very convenient to everything in Amsterdam. We arrived in the morning and were allowed to check in a bit earlier than the 1pm check in time,   which was very nice of our hosts.  
During the week of our stay, the roof developed a leak into the bedroom.  We reported it and within a few days they repaired the leak.  We were appropriately compensated for the inconvenience .  
The apartment could have benefited from a bit more attention to detail,  like  drinking glasses in the kitchen and working light bulbs in the bathroom,   All in all, it was a positive experience and we would stay there again.
